  {
    "index": 3,
    "hash": "vEu37sHx8HcSRFrGFWlpkse80Ms=",
    "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z",
    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "The Bee Reactor Adapter repo publishes two independent packages:\n\n| Package | npm | Role |\n|---------|-----|------|\n| `packages/adapter` | `@liberuum-org/bee-reactor-adapter` | Core adapter: SwarmClient, SwarmChannel, ACT-encrypted sharing, PSS/GSOC chat, postage stamps |\n| `packages/connect` | `@liberuum-org/connect` | Fork of Powerhouse Connect with Swarm landing page, settings UI, and chat panel |\n\nExample integration into any Powerhouse project:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"dependencies\": {\n    \"@liberuum-org/bee-reactor-adapter\": \"0.23.0\"\n  },\n  \"overrides\": {\n    \"@powerhousedao/connect\": \"npm:@liberuum-org/connect@6.0.0-dev.174-swarm.1\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\nEach package publishes independently with `npm publish --otp=CODE` (the connect fork uses `--tag swarm`). Builds are driven by `npx tsc` for the adapter and `bun run build` for connect.",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:27.000Z"
    }
  },
